      <title>OpenAI 的企业采用和苹果的机器人野心 |彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/openai-s-enterprise-adoption-and-apple-s-robot-ambitions-bloomberg-technology</link>
